00:02:57.540 --> 00:03:02.290
This is one of those laws on which we’ve
built our entire understanding of the universe,

00:03:02.290 --> 00:03:06.040
anything that would upend it would rewrite
multiple scientific disciplines.

00:03:06.040 --> 00:03:10.340
A machine that can keep itself running forever
and could power your toaster to boot would

00:03:10.340 --> 00:03:13.150
be more than 100% efficient.

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:17.660
In other words, it would get something from
nothing, and from everything we’ve ever

00:03:17.660 --> 00:03:21.270
seen ever, that’s just not possible.

